name: ATimeTravel
description:
Hello! Time is running out and we have to save it. You have to go through those aliens with one eye and not be shot, the goal being to get to the other ship and press a button to save time. That ship is also a spaceship that can travel through time and space.

Controls:
WASD - travel
Space - jump
F - lantern
Left click - confirm

!The game may suffer from updates.!
